                    <strong>
                     We are proud to  cater all the Pharmaceutical’s markets of India by our Quality Results and  strategically developed strong distribution system with our successful sales  team. We thank doctors, Customers, distributors, Pharmacists and health care  institutions who posed trust in the quality and efficacy of our products. The  company is continuously evaluating new prospects to add to the existing  portfolio in India. At Manstar we have dedicated ourselves to human  health.
                     <br />
                    </strong>
                    <br />
                    We are committed to provide quality  medication at affordable prices to the patients across the nation with a view  to help bring down the healthcare costs. We are confident that our efforts  would see the Company grow from strength to strength in the global (branded and  generic) space in the years to come.
                    <br />
                    <br />
                    As we move ahead we are determined to capitalize on the new opportunities based  on our strong fundamentals of innovation, entrepreneurship and aggressive  marketing. We remain committed to enhancing the value of various customers,  employees and suppliers as we actively pursue our strategy of growth through  organic and inorganic means.
                    <br />
                    <br />
                    May God give us more  strength to build better India and our industry with full dedication and  commitment and we must continue to believe in continues innovation, bringing  new molecules, advance machinery and equipments, bringing new technology, and  adopt modern ways of marketing.
                    <br />
                    <br />
                    As we step into the next phase, we are driven by our ambition, willing to  invest in the growth of our people and business, marching towards the new  horizon of national and finally global leadership.
                    <strong>
                     <br />
                     <br />
                     Managing Director
                    </strong>
                   </span>
